 <body>
  <div class="notice danger" data-draft-warning="true">
   UNREVIEWED MACHINE TRANSLATION DRAFT (fr). Do not use for medical guidance, sharing, printing, or training until fluent local reviewers verify all emergency numbers, doses, timings, and local guidance against the English source.
